data.description: AMAZING NEW PRICE! Full-brick home in the popular, gated community of Stonechase, in Pace, FL! This home is located in Phase I, with mature trees, finished homes, and a great neighborhood feel! Enter the front door and you’ll be greeted by the soaring ceiling heights of the great room, a formal dining room to your left, and a laundry room to the right (with Samsung washer/dryer included!) The great room features a wood burning fireplace, plant ledges, and cable/electrical outlets to place a HUGE TV over the mantel. The fully-equipped kitchen has: a smooth-top range, dishwasher, built-in microwave (all GE), and Samsung refrigerator. In addition, there is a large pantry, breakfast bar, and addl. dining area! The primary suite is split and comes with a lighted trey ceiling and generously-sized bath with: double vanities, garden tub, separate shower, and enormous walk-in closet! You’ll feel like you are at the spa! The 2 additional bedrooms share a hall bath and have painted accent walls. Both have wide, double-door closets for extra storage. Throughout the home, you will find prairie-style double-pane windows with tilt sashes and tile flooring, except for the bedrooms. Your fenced backyard has tall pine trees for shade, a covered patio, and space for the addition of conversation areas, fire pit, or more! Also included: recessed lighting, double car garage, sprinkler system, and oil rubbed bronze fixtures throughout. A newer HVAC unit with UV light was installed in 2020. Stonechase has underground electric, a picnic area, and a main gate with guard (one of the few communities with this feature in our region!) Close to top-rated schools, and just a short drive from the airport, Downtown Pensacola, and the sugar white sands of Pensacola Beach! Schedule your appointment for this MUST-SEE property today!
